  "title": "AB03 -  Conveyancing Legal Associate (Junior)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position title: Junior Conveyancing Lawyer</strong></p><p>Working Days: 5 days<br />Working Timing: 9:00 am to 6:00 pm<br />Working Location: Telok Ayer Street <br />Starting Salary: $5,500</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities & Duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and review legal documents related to property transactions. These documents include sale and purchase agreements and loan agreements.</li><li>You will provide advice to clients on all aspects of buying or selling property. This includes legal issues, financial considerations, and contract matters.</li><li>Engage in negotiations with the other party’s lawyer for the Option to Purchase (OTP). Provide advice to clients on the conveyancing process and their rights and obligations.</li><li>Liaise with various parties involved in the transaction, including real estate agents, mortgage lenders, and other relevant stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications and Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree in Law </li><li>0-3 years of Post-Qualification Experience (PQE) in conveyancing or related<br />legal work.</li><li>Familiarity with property laws and conveyancing procedures.</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
